title: Old Man's Aches & Young's Mistakes
itunes:title: Old Man's Aches & Young's Mistakes
description:
THU 6/30 - Charlamagne is feeling the burn after his birthday celebration, with aches and pains only built for old men. Meanwhile, Nick Young can't turn the charm or the cameras off in the latest twist of his failed romance with Iggy Azalea. Don't know who's hurting worse this morning: Swaggy P or Old Man C?
